  h4 Grid
  p Grid is built on top of <a href='http://css-tricks.com/snippets/css/a-guide-to-flexbox/'>flexbox</a>. Cells (<code>grid-flex-cell</code>) will have the width of <code>100%</code> below <code>481px</code> and automatically calculated width (depending on cell count) above that breakpoint. Grid must be placed within <code>div</code> with <code>container</code> class.

  p Instead of relying on calculation of widths depending on number of cells you can use helper fraction classes: <code>grid-flex-cell-1of4</code>, <code>grid-flex-cell-1of3</code>, <code>grid-flex-cell-1of2</code>. The width of other cells will be calculated automatically by the browser. 

  .grid-flex-container

    .grid-flex-cell
      p 1/2
    .grid-flex-cell
      p 1/2

  .grid-flex-container

    .grid-flex-cell
      p 1/3
    .grid-flex-cell
      p 1/3
    .grid-flex-cell
      p 1/3

  .grid-flex-container

    .grid-flex-cell
